<h1>Overview</h1>
<p>Lotus japonicus accession Miyakojima MG-20 is a reference legume, 472M bp, 2n = 12. 
The euchromatic region has been sequenced BAC/TAC by BAC/TAC and selected TAC mixture sequencing.</p>

